{"tid":2422033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"找12-15歲學生填問卷（5名幸運兒每人獲得港幣$100元＋中文DSE實戰5星星作文）","createTime":"2021-02-25T02:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T04:27:40.000Z","uid":393299,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a2451232ca2c54ccf94c763a2ce365f1b4b32e55","tid":2422033,"uid":393299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"【隨機抽取5名幸運兒每人獲得港幣$100元】<br />\n【完成問卷可提供中文DSE實戰5星星作文】<br />\n您好，我是香港中文大學心理學系學生，現正進行「父母管教如何影響學業成績」的研究，招募年齡介乎12至15歲的香港學生完成十分鐘的問卷🙏🏻。由於是次研究的sample size 不大，所以中獎機率大為提高。<br />\n<br />\n【參加者要求】<br />\n- 年齡介乎12至15歲的香港學生<br />\n- 具備基本閱讀中文的能力<br />\n- 與父母同住<br />\n<br />\n【研究流程】<br />\n1. 點擊以下連結，完成家長授權。<br />\n<a href=\"http://esurvey.psy.cuhk.edu.hk/jfe/form/SV_71yOy2pp889jA3P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fesurvey.psy.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_71yOy2pp889jA3P&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=549eb6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://esurvey.psy.cuhk.edu.hk/jfe/form/SV_71yOy2pp889jA3P</a><br />\n2. 讓子女繼續填妥問卷。<br />\n3. 等待抽獎結果，將透過電郵通知。<br />\n<br />\n如您對本研究計劃有任何疑問，歡迎致電54218750或電郵至1155108781@link.cuhk.edu.hk與本計劃的研究員聯絡。謝謝🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️！"},{"pid":"57870ceab1262f9e4adec1e15f05196cf122f45b","tid":2422033,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:12:23.000Z","msg":"25歲但想做"},{"pid":"495f279239e0c632213e0854ec3f07ab1f0e250d","tid":2422033,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"點解唔出mass mail"},{"pid":"ad505e7c9c44575bf62e014add6f764ad22b8268","tid":2422033,"uid":218716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"太少la, $10000 一個la."}]}